api/rest/dialogueService

[POST] dialogue/create  // this method provide adding new dialogue, or adding new massage for existing dialogue.
In this case dialogue will be spots by list of members and subject.

[POST] dialogue/id/{id}/message/create // this method provide adding new message to existing dialogue.
Id in path is a dialogue id.

[POST] dialogue/read/id/{id}  // this method provide getting all message from existing dialogue.
[POST] dialogue/read/all  // this method provide getting all dialogs for logged user.
[POST] dialogue/update/id/{id}  // this method provide update dialog.

JSON example

 {
     "id" : "5616c91e06f4830486a5092c",
     "subject" : "sabj!",
     "members" : [
         {
             "id" : "5613d146fa12fded9736f671",
             "name":"roro" // Do not sand, autocomplete in read time.
         }
     ],
     "messages" : [
         {
             "authorId" : "5613d146fa12fded9736f671", //create automatically, do not send. Take id of current logged user.
             "date" : ISODate("2015-10-08T19:50:54.367Z"), //create automatically, do not send. Take time of creation.
             "message" : "Hello Andrei"
         }
     ]
 }